Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.25,0:00:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名偵探柯南60分鐘特別節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.17,0:00:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的案件有些嚇人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.07,0:00:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠離塵囂的山中寺廟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.69,0:00:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了不可思議的殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.88,0:00:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詭異的霧天狗傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.63,0:00:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何被迷霧所籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.15,0:00:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真相永遠只有一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.69,0:01:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧天狗傳說殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.20,0:01:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山櫻真的好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.79,0:01:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看 那邊的山上也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.85,0:01:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喧囂的城市裡盛開的櫻花雖然不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.80,0:01:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在如此遠離塵囂的深山中樸實綻放著的山櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.92,0:02:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才擁有真正的櫻花之美啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這個大叔就只會耍嘴皮子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.29,0:02:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.60,0:02:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們大老遠跑到深山裡來真是值得啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.07,0:02:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有枉費租車過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.72,0:02:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧 拍一張作為留念吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.66,0:02:16.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來來 兩個人都站那邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.05,0:02:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.46,0:02:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它設定為自動拍攝 爸爸你也來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.87,0:02:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.87,0:02:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫江戶川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.14,0:02:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大叔是自稱名偵探的毛利小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.39,0:02:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我青梅竹馬的同班同學毛利蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.15,0:02:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我為什麼會是同班同學啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.20,0:02:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上我的真實身份是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.79,0:02:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中生偵探工藤新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.88,0:02:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是因那天而起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.79,0:02:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小蘭去多羅碧加樂園遊玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.68,0:02:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現一個神秘組織正在進行非法交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.89,0:02:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣男子 伏特加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.91,0:03:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.80,0:03:03.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我背後悄悄靠近的另一名黑衣男子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.84,0:03:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.81,0:03:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我打倒在地之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.17,0:03:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我服下組織開發中的藥物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.95,0:03:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體好燙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.69,0:03:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨頭好像要融化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.31,0:03:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.04,0:03:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被巡警的聲音叫醒的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體居然縮小了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.96,0:03:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 只要查到那些傢伙的老巢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.14,0:03:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將藥弄到手就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.80,0:03:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.24,0:03:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他們知道你還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.03,0:03:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會再來要你的命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.93,0:03:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你跟我兩個人的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.46,0:03:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能跟任何人說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.26,0:03:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然小蘭也不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.33,0:03:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位大伯是發明家阿笠博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.08,0:04:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣身體縮小的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.29,0:04:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便化名為江戶川柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.63,0:04:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了掌握那些傢伙的線索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.69,0:04:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就寄宿在父親是私家偵探的小蘭家中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.63,0:04:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這個大叔簡直就是個糊塗偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.88,0:04:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不下去的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.01,0:04:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用阿笠博士發明的手錶型麻醉槍讓他睡著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.69,0:04:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再利用蝴蝶結型變聲器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.77,0:04:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解決了大大小小的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.92,0:04:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到今天仍以柯南的身份生活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.92,0:04:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟何時才能變回原樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.93,0:04:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.10,0:04:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船到橋頭自然直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.41,0:04:43.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼要回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.69,0:04:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這前面有條近路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.85,0:04:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就走那條路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.32,0:04:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題嗎 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.89,0:04:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會迷路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.16,0:04:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.10,0:04:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.30,0:05:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才問你啊 到底有沒有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.92,0:05:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不但迷路了 而且還爆胎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.86,0:05:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易有了個好心情現在全沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.97,0:05:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.13,0:05:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨也來作對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.88,0:05:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.99,0:05:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離山腳還有二、三十公裡呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.71,0:05:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.49,0:05:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方又不像會有人居住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.67,0:05:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在車裡過一夜吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要在這種地方露宿呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.42,0:05:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆胎能不能修好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.97,0:05:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有備用胎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.92,0:05:40.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然連爆兩次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.18,0:05:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真倒楣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.53,0:05:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 那小子去哪兒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.90,0:05:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.59,0:05:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.67,0:05:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南你在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.94,0:05:55.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.74,0:05:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥 是鳥啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.91,0:06:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.54,0:06:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳剛才為什麼叫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.57,0:06:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.72,0:06:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來　你去哪裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.77,0:06:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能隨便亂走哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.87,0:06:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 在這前面找到一座寺廟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.17,0:06:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定有誰住在裡面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.87,0:06:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.72,0:06:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方居然會有寺廟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.34,0:06:28.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是得救了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.12,0:06:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們過去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.13,0:06:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,建在這地方挺嚇人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.16,0:06:43.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山泥寺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.42,0:06:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就只能住這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.20,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.07,0:06:53.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.24,0:06:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們有何貴幹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.63,0:07:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你們到這裡來幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.26,0:07:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們又是報社或是電視臺的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.05,0:07:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.21,0:07:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是你們這些骯髒的人來的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.69,0:07:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.55,0:07:18.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們經過這裡時不巧爆胎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.83,0:07:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能借住一宿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.61,0:07:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你們想住這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.51,0:07:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是　如果不方便的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.39,0:07:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們馬上就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.02,0:07:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想借宿就早點說嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.39,0:07:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你們是那些想採訪那個的人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.37,0:07:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼 這裡的一些傳說而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.21,0:07:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齋飯一頓 順帶參拜寺廟留宿一晚費用成人一萬日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.14,0:07:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩八千日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.07,0:07:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我們寺裡還兼做住宿生意的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.98,0:07:56.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一萬日元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意的話就算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到山腳要步行六個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.15,0:08:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們慢慢走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.14,0:08:05.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 我還沒說不住嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.45,0:08:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.69,0:08:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個 難得有客人來囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.00,0:08:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.19,0:08:12.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒說要住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.01,0:08:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我冒昧 你們還是住下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.71,0:08:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨天那傢伙搞不好也會出沒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.77,0:08:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.86,0:08:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有熊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.64,0:08:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.85,0:08:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那麼可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.19,0:08:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出沒在暴雨和黑夜 專門掠奪人的靈魂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.77,0:08:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古代的魔物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.09,0:08:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧天狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.79,0:08:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧…霧天狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.07,0:08:49.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.13,0:08:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是禁語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.78,0:08:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了剛才的話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.41,0:08:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.09,0:09:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我來介紹一下在寺中修行的四位修行僧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.47,0:09:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是四人中修行年頭最長的大師兄寬念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.44,0:09:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.77,0:09:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胃口很大 善於料理又是大力士的屯念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.01,0:09:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手很巧將寺裡的木工活一手包辦的木念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.71,0:09:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.38,0:09:25.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年剛入寺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.98,0:09:30.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身材矮小 學習相當用功又很聰明的秀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.53,0:09:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.77,0:09:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後我是這個寺廟的住持天永
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.14,0:09:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 屯念和木念去準備晚飯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.41,0:09:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寬念和秀念帶這些客人參觀一下寺廟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.69,0:09:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像必須要住下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.46,0:09:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.65,0:09:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,租車延長費加住宿費 這個月又花光了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.62,0:09:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是山泥寺的鎮寺佛像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.31,0:10:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好端莊啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.96,0:10:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.96,0:10:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾位也葬在這兒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑啦 開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.80,0:10:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.81,0:10:11.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 這邊請
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.61,0:10:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.11,0:10:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個帶鎖的房間是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是倉庫嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.68,0:10:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟 那裡是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.79,0:10:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 不過是個小房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.71,0:10:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.07,0:10:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高的天花板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.26,0:10:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這房間是做什麼用的 小師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.75,0:10:45.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是修行的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.43,0:10:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前違反戒律的和尚會被關在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.78,0:10:53.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他反省
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.86,0:10:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得建得那麼牢固
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.59,0:10:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.62,0:11:00.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓人爬上去還塗了漆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.63,0:11:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼只有這面牆上木板的顏色不一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.05,0:11:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是因為那個事件把這裡弄壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.21,0:11:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木念事後修補留下的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧 寬念師兄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.28,0:11:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.37,0:11:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我來這個寺之前發生的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.64,0:11:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情況我不是很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.75,0:11:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是霧天狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.62,0:11:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說了秀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.03,0:11:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事怎麼能和客人講呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.15,0:11:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.75,0:11:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.72,0:11:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瀑布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 要不要去看看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.18,0:11:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這個房間的旁邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南 快點來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.44,0:11:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壯觀哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.86,0:11:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瀑布真的就在眼前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.05,0:11:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看 瀑布越過扶手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往裡面沖進來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.33,0:11:59.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.94,0:12:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然堵上了那些縫隙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心滑倒的話還是很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.19,0:12:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是櫻花的花瓣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.13,0:12:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山上的櫻花隨著瀑布被沖刷下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有情調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.76,0:12:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.39,0:12:18.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想晚飯應該準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.42,0:12:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以為和尚都很死板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.61,0:12:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到還有娛樂的時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾休息的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家會去海邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著寺裡的橡皮艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.30,0:12:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有海灘球去玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.07,0:12:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住持一看到穿著比基尼的美女連魂都沒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.01,0:12:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡說些無聊的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.49,0:12:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從剛才開始我就很想知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.59,0:12:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧天狗是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟你是從哪裡聽來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.25,0:12:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 是我說漏嘴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.18,0:12:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住持大師…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.40,0:13:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是無聊的古代傳說而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.92,0:13:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗會在雨夜如霧一般默默潛入村中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.94,0:13:10.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用勢不可擋的強大力量打破牆壁擄走村民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.62,0:13:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用它那穿梭在空中的雙腿 將人懸掛到高大的樹上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.09,0:13:19.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後啃食人肉的古代魔物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.47,0:13:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被擄走的都是些細皮嫩肉的年輕女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.39,0:13:30.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 剛好就像小姐你這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.05,0:13:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這只是傳說而已 沒必要擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.73,0:13:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.86,0:13:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.62,0:13:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也並非全是空穴來風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.02,0:13:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在兩年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.15,0:13:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了一樁與傳說同樣詭異的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.34,0:13:50.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.60,0:13:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.62,0:13:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他們說說事件的詳細情況吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.72,0:13:59.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為叔叔不是名偵探毛利小五郎嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.40,0:14:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會發現什麼哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.05,0:14:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名偵探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.06,0:14:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.43,0:14:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.86,0:14:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就是那位有名的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.43,0:14:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是您也許真的能解開那個事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.83,0:14:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我們說 偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.65,0:14:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上在兩年前有位年輕的修行僧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.26,0:14:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們給我閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.23,0:14:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規定了不可以再提那個事件 你們難道忘了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.06,0:14:24.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是住持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.73,0:14:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.73,0:14:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回房間準備睡覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.16,0:14:38.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偵探先生 我借你們住宿一晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.39,0:14:43.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天一早請速速離開本寺 請別見怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.23,0:15:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.64,0:15:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會真的有什麼天狗吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.83,0:15:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不會有囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.00,0:15:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳難道認為河童、鬼怪是存在的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗跟那些是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.02,0:15:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是人類編造出來想像中的生物罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.46,0:15:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.60,0:15:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本在很久很久以前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.28,0:15:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會發出打雷那樣聲響的流星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.27,0:15:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被中國人叫做天上的狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.08,0:15:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是天狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.25,0:15:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在中國這種流星墜落下來的現象被認為是不吉利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.07,0:15:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也流傳到了日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.07,0:15:39.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狗就從詭異的現象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.49,0:15:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來就演變成擁有詭異神力的狀似狐狸的妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.11,0:15:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明只是個小鬼 知道的怪事還真不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.66,0:15:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦 之前電視上播過這個節目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.84,0:15:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以小蘭姐姐 根本不用害怕哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.36,0:16:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭 我怎麼會害怕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.85,0:16:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 睡覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.69,0:16:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上如果害怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.31,0:16:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑽到我的被窩裡來也沒關係哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.91,0:16:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.26,0:16:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.63,0:16:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如果害怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.89,0:16:27.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑽到我的被窩裡來也沒關係哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.30,0:16:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專吃那些細皮嫩肉的年輕女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.07,0:17:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 就像小姐妳這樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.42,0:17:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭妳搞什麼 三更半夜叫醒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.20,0:17:16.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.17,0:17:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還是很在意那個事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.39,0:17:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.57,0:17:25.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們如果不想講 問了也沒用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.34,0:17:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能會出現霧天狗嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.89,0:17:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.10,0:17:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們對我有什麼意見嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.28,0:17:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 你自己還不是很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.74,0:17:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.05,0:17:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個面具是怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.71,0:17:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是掛在廁所裡的裝飾品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.33,0:17:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.31,0:17:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.02,0:17:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.97,0:17:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.52,0:17:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚安 寬念師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.90,0:17:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.13,0:18:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把這個帶出來了 怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.58,0:18:02.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 妳就戴起來好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.40,0:18:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜她所賜我是徹底醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.41,0:18:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位 早飯準備好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.44,0:18:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 馬上就去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.39,0:18:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來很睏啊 秀念師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.23,0:18:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天我讀書讀到很晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.22,0:18:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.51,0:18:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木念師父也沒睡好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.70,0:18:41.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不都是因為你昨晚的尖叫聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.36,0:18:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直不放心沒辦法睡覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.02,0:18:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.97,0:18:47.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.22,0:18:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屯念他一晚沒合過眼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.06,0:18:56.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 住持和寬念師父呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.97,0:19:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寬念因為沒看到住持去找他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.70,0:19:04.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正一定是昨晚喝醉酒…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.05,0:19:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.07,0:19:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛…剛才是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.19,0:19:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寬念的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.64,0:19:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是從修行的房間傳來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.36,0:19:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.45,0:19:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.19,0:19:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天…天永和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.57,0:19:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吊而死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.67,0:19:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這個寺廟的住持天永和尚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.36,0:19:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死亡推斷時間是昨夜十點至十二點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.67,0:19:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現屍體的是寺裡的修行僧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.85,0:19:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寬念師父 是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.98,0:19:52.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為一大早就沒見到住持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.71,0:19:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.12,0:19:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就在這個修行的房間發現住持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.52,0:20:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到他的慘叫趕來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.68,0:20:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是湊巧在這裡借宿的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.84,0:20:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我毛利小五郎 目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.18,0:20:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 你的叫聲真是驚人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.59,0:20:13.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寬念師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.97,0:20:15.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒你厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.24,0:20:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寬念師父真會找啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.84,0:20:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為住持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.10,0:20:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被吊在那麼高的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.15,0:20:28.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的話 根本發現不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.53,0:20:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是很可疑啊 寬念師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.52,0:20:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是你原先就知道住持會被吊在天花板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.52,0:20:41.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.72,0:20:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被發現是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.36,0:20:47.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.97,0:20:49.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在兩年前這個房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.85,0:20:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也發生了幾乎一模一樣的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.38,0:20:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩…兩年前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.93,0:20:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是我負責的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.50,0:21:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死者好像是叫做忠念的修行僧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:01.73,0:21:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而發現屍體的是寬念和木念兩人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.18,0:21:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在梅雨季節的一個雨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.40,0:21:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個房間修行的忠念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.39,0:21:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在牆上破壞出了一個大洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.96,0:21:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就不見了蹤影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.17,0:21:23.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們找了三天三夜也沒找到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.32,0:21:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在我們認為他已經逃出寺外而放棄尋找的第四天早上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.58,0:21:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了修理房間的牆壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.07,0:21:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟寬念來到這個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.19,0:21:33.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不經意抬頭看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.95,0:21:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠念被吊在了天花板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.79,0:21:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上回被破壞的牆壁這次也壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.10,0:21:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本以為是忠念為了逃出房間而破壞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.79,0:21:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是房間的門又沒有上鎖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.98,0:22:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而…而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.39,0:22:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來我們請附近的木工來修理外牆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.72,0:22:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說只靠一個人要把牆壁破壞出這麼大的一個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.43,0:22:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用一天的時間是很難辦到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.14,0:22:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以輕易做到這種事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.23,0:22:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有擁有怪力的古代魔物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.10,0:22:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧…霧天狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.32,0:22:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧…霧天狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:29.01,0:22:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:30.59,0:22:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世間怎麼會有那種妖怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.59,0:22:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.67,0:22:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然和兩年前一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.07,0:22:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩側的橫樑上積了厚厚一層灰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.90,0:22:42.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有被擦拭過的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.92,0:22:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中間的橫樑雖然掉了一些灰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.85,0:22:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有繩子綁在上面並無其他痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.40,0:22:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次是不是也是自殺呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.40,0:22:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.78,0:22:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是爬上去的話 就得像那個員警一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.03,0:23:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綁上繩子後爬上橫樑 光是這樣就很吃力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.21,0:23:04.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還要把一個人搬到那麼高的地方就又要另當別論了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.08,0:23:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死去的忠念師父跟住持的體型差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.93,0:23:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要背著他用繩子爬上去根本是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.63,0:23:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果事先將繩子套在他的脖子上之後再吊上去的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.59,0:23:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫樑上一定會有繩子摩擦的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.33,0:23:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是自己先爬上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:20.98,0:23:23.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再將屍體拉上來是有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.79,0:23:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是能呆的地方就只有那根細細的橫樑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.63,0:23:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也不太可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.20,0:23:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.24,0:23:32.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩下自己一個人爬上橫樑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.46,0:23:35.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在上面綁好繩圈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.53,0:23:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把繩圈套在自己脖子上再跳下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.84,0:23:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多餘的繩子以及有可能用來鑿牆的斧子都掉在了地上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.00,0:23:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是錯不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.62,0:23:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.06,0:23:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與上回一樣可疑之處還是這面牆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.01,0:23:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不知道這是怎麼弄的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.24,0:23:58.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是破壞牆壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.81,0:24:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者在天花板上吊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.25,0:24:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是在模仿那個古老傳說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.78,0:24:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是在向我們暗示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.63,0:24:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是被那飛翔於空中的霧天狗奪走靈魂的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.52,0:24:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是會引起騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.74,0:24:17.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.00,0:24:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這面被破壞的牆好奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.48,0:24:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡本來應該是有個氣窗對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.68,0:24:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牆上被破壞出了那麼大的一個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.57,0:24:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近卻連牆壁的碎片都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.87,0:24:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:36.66,0:24:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.62,0:24:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟他是個將自殺偽裝成霧天狗的傑作的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.81,0:24:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在想什麼 我們是不可能知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.06,0:24:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.98,0:24:51.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.66,0:24:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得她好像是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.83,0:24:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住持的孫女菊乃小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.70,0:25:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 為什麼會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.82,0:25:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前趴在忠念屍體旁哭泣的好像也是她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.28,0:25:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前她還經常會到這個寺裡來玩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.36,0:25:16.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個事件發生後就再也沒來過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:16.59,0:25:18.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 爺爺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.54,0:25:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.15,0:25:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是菊乃小姐的丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:24.75,0:25:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上個月剛結的婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:27.72,0:25:30.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是個大寺廟的繼承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.69,0:25:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人從小就訂下婚約了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:34.10,0:25:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前從住持那兒聽到這件事時 真是嚇了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:39.28,0:25:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本一直以為菊乃小姐會和忠念在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:43.98,0:25:45.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說死去的忠念師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:47.03,0:25:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個簡直親如兄妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:50.94,0:25:55.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠念一定是因為聽到菊乃要結婚的事受到相當大的打擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:56.68,0:25:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才會做出那樣的傻事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:59.00,0:26:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說住持一直對那件事感到內疚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.05,0:26:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在菊乃小姐結婚之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.06,0:26:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇了和忠念一樣的死法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:08.78,0:26:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:10.78,0:26:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.77,0:26:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定找得到遺書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:13.90,0:26:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家分頭找找看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:20.23,0:26:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:21.84,0:26:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是那樣嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:23.84,0:26:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算再怎麼想裝扮成傳說的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:26.76,0:26:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有人特地想在那種地方上吊嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:29.91,0:26:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:30.96,0:26:32.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在牆上破壞出了那麼大的一個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:34.18,0:26:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是自殺的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:36.60,0:26:39.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個大洞是某個作案手法留下的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:40.61,0:26:43.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的事件和兩年前的事件手法應該如出一轍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:44.02,0:26:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:45.20,0:26:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠念師父和住持是被同一個人所殺害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:50.05,0:26:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嘛 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:54.48,0:26:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀念師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:56.56,0:27:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人好像是一年前剛剛進寺的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:04.09,0:27:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼細的手臂是沒法弄出那麼大的洞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.88,0:27:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀念師父 我記得你說昨晚看書看到很晚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:14.33,0:27:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了三點多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:16.45,0:27:18.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這期間有沒有注意到發生過什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:20.10,0:27:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說有人悄悄溜出他的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:23.97,0:27:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者是打破什麼東西的怪聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:26.34,0:27:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者誰的慘叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:28.00,0:27:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我什麼也沒聽到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:30.80,0:27:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚很安靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:33.76,0:27:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的什麼都沒有嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:36.18,0:27:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住持的房間雖然離得比較遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:38.57,0:27:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家的房間都在隔壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:40.82,0:27:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果發生什麼事的話我一定會察覺到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:43.70,0:27:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:45.23,0:27:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在懷疑大家嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:47.29,0:27:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:47.96,0:27:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 秀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:49.78,0:27:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你別磨蹭了 一起幫忙來找找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:06.71,0:28:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 還差一點 加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:10.14,0:28:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繩子要是鬆了 真不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:12.92,0:28:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:14.55,0:28:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:16.44,0:28:19.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那扇窗就在住持死亡的房間上面對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:22.49,0:28:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有可能從這裡把人搬過去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:27.27,0:28:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該不太可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:28.50,0:28:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不在橫樑上面留下痕跡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:31.26,0:28:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:31.99,0:28:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要在那麼細的橫樑上背著一個人做什麼事的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:35.08,0:28:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也太不現實了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:42.92,0:28:44.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個裂縫怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:46.72,0:28:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切口那麼不整齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:48.74,0:28:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別的地方都很切得很整齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:54.32,0:28:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:55.86,0:28:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過切口已經很舊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:57.78,0:28:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很早以前弄的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:01.19,0:29:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縫隙邊還黏著不少櫻花花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:04.59,0:29:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:06.50,0:29:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:09.09,0:29:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:10.78,0:29:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:12.57,0:29:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:14.26,0:29:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要找那個小弟弟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:15.46,0:29:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他向我問了去寺下樹林的路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:17.40,0:29:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:31.54,0:29:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現場來看唯一不見的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:33.88,0:29:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被破壞的牆壁和木板的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:37.26,0:29:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人如果真的從那裡將它們扔下來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:40.85,0:29:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會掉在這裡的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:43.55,0:29:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能找到它們說不定就能知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:46.16,0:29:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人為什麼不得不扔掉它們的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:49.24,0:29:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:50.13,0:29:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作案手法也會明朗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:01.77,0:30:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:02.66,0:30:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是木板的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:04.48,0:30:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是那個氣窗的一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:08.18,0:30:09.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面黏著膠帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:10.32,0:30:11.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:12.76,0:30:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在這兒幹嘛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:15.46,0:30:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:17.19,0:30:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛拿著那塊髒兮兮的木板啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:19.18,0:30:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點把它丟掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:20.47,0:30:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能丟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:26.62,0:30:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 今天差不多該收隊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:33.21,0:30:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菊乃小姐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:35.64,0:30:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她陪著她爺爺的屍體去了警察局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:39.03,0:30:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 最後還是沒能找到遺書啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:42.19,0:30:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼關係吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:43.89,0:30:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正肯定是自殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:46.51,0:30:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:47.70,0:30:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:49.62,0:30:51.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚一定發生了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:51.36,0:30:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這間屋子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:52.42,0:30:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了超乎想像的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:55.73,0:30:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被巨大的力量破壞的牆壁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:59.14,0:31:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切口不齊的木板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:01.32,0:31:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:02.08,0:31:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遺棄在樹林裡的氣窗碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:04.80,0:31:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有碎片上黏著的膠帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:07.82,0:31:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將它們聯繫起來的關鍵究竟是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:19.51,0:31:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:22.99,0:31:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:24.14,0:31:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:25.05,0:31:26.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手所使用的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:27.39,0:31:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是這樣 那麼兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:29.00,0:31:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概一個晚上都得待在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:33.62,0:31:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:34.95,0:31:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那個人才會對那件事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:37.80,0:31:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來兇手 就是那個人沒錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:46.26,0:31:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能犯罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:47.86,0:31:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是兇手在凶案現場製造出的犯罪藝術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:52.85,0:31:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次展示這項藝術的舞臺是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:55.17,0:31:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花飛舞的山中古寺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:57.87,0:31:59.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手將繩索高高地吊在了天花板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:00.14,0:32:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寺廟的住持被人勒住脖子上吊而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:03.47,0:32:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然沒有發現任何被拉上去的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:06.60,0:32:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說常人根本無法做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:09.72,0:32:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:10.77,0:32:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手利用某種力量 懸浮到了空中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:14.01,0:32:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:14.91,0:32:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那擁有魔翅翱翔於天際的霧天狗一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:18.97,0:32:20.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在住持遇害的房間地板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:21.17,0:32:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一段多餘的繩子和一把斧子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:23.95,0:32:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更不可思議的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:25.32,0:32:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那面有氣窗的牆壁明明被破壞出了很大的一個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:28.39,0:32:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而木板和碎片卻不翼而飛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:31.31,0:32:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:32.11,0:32:33.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一塊切口不齊的木板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:34.19,0:32:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被遺棄在樹林裡的氣窗的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:37.14,0:32:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有碎片上黏著的膠帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:39.76,0:32:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將它們聯繫起來的關鍵是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:47.56,0:32:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:48.76,0:32:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:50.47,0:32:52.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手所使用的手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:52.73,0:32:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是這樣 那麼兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:54.25,0:32:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概一個晚上都得待在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:57.49,0:32:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:58.87,0:33:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那個人才會對那件事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:01.52,0:33:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:03.17,0:33:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個人沒錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:06.74,0:33:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 警部大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:09.39,0:33:10.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 我知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:10.86,0:33:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒用警車把你們送回家就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:13.51,0:33:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 在警察們收隊前將這件事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:17.17,0:33:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便把你在森林裡爆胎的車的鑰匙也交給我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:22.67,0:33:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒我讓手下將它拉走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:25.55,0:33:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前的幾個案子你也幫了不少忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:28.95,0:33:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:32.82,0:33:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙我拿走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:34.35,0:33:35.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住 小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:37.20,0:33:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:38.51,0:33:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小鬼跑哪兒去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:41.84,0:33:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木板不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:47.54,0:33:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然自己滑倒暈過去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:50.51,0:33:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好 省得我再用麻醉槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:56.10,0:33:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個鈕扣是個小型擴音器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:59.30,0:34:01.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新一你可以通過蝴蝶結麥克風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:01.62,0:34:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用無線電將聲音傳出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:04.66,0:34:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先把這個貼上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:06.27,0:34:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:08.55,0:34:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是警察叔叔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:09.81,0:34:11.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以隨便進來哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:11.47,0:34:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來得正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:12.87,0:34:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛利叔叔說讓大家在案發的房間集合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:17.60,0:34:19.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 警察叔叔你有膠帶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:21.15,0:34:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膠帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:23.16,0:34:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:24.27,0:34:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你已經知道兇手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:27.00,0:34:30.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是把住持之死偽裝成自殺的兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:31.56,0:34:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住持是被繩子勒住脖子 吊在天花板上死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:37.65,0:34:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果說這是某個人故意布下的局
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:40.29,0:34:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是怎麼辦到的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:42.99,0:34:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在橫樑上沒有發現往上拉的痕跡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:47.94,0:34:50.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不會留下什麼痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:50.55,0:34:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:51.43,0:34:53.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在天花板橫樑正下方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:53.33,0:34:55.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和住持一起漂浮到空中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:55.63,0:34:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再把繩圈套在住持頭上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:58.92,0:35:00.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂浮到空中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:01.73,0:35:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是霧天狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:03.42,0:35:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類怎麼可能辦得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:06.08,0:35:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到這個聲音了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:08.99,0:35:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瀑布的聲音吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:10.46,0:35:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 它就從我身邊的天窗流過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:15.67,0:35:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要將瀑布的水從天窗引入房內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:18.83,0:35:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓整個房間充滿水的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:22.21,0:35:25.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不認為這樣就能浮到空中了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:25.92,0:35:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個房間充滿水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:29.86,0:35:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吹牛也要打打草稿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:32.13,0:35:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:33.13,0:35:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是兇手還是被害人全身都會濕透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:35.30,0:35:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我們卻沒有在屍體身上發現被淋濕的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:38.39,0:35:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用橡皮艇啊 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:40.51,0:35:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橡…橡皮艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:42.54,0:35:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寬念師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:43.62,0:35:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你說過這個寺裡有艘橡皮艇是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:49.18,0:35:51.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將屍體放在橡皮艇上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:51.79,0:35:54.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再在上面蓋上一張塑膠布之類的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:54.34,0:35:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能滴水不沾地將他送到天花板下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:57.50,0:35:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:58.78,0:36:00.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天窗畢竟離瀑布還有一段距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:01.36,0:36:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能那麼巧把水引進來嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:09.00,0:36:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用木板就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:11.02,0:36:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要將木板的那些縫隙用膠帶封上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:14.44,0:36:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水就能被順利地從瀑布引到屋內了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:17.01,0:36:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:18.24,0:36:20.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這塊木板的切口參差不齊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:21.16,0:36:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了配合長度而留下的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:24.82,0:36:28.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在我認為是貼膠帶的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:28.59,0:36:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並排沾上了一些櫻花的花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:32.01,0:36:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被瀑布從山上沖下來的櫻花花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:43.41,0:36:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 櫻花花瓣不僅僅留在了木板上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:47.85,0:36:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目暮警官的腳邊應該也會飄落幾片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:53.81,0:36:55.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是兇手把水抽幹之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:55.91,0:36:58.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附著在牆上的櫻花花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:00.75,0:37:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:02.08,0:37:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將住持勒死後搬到這個房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:05.16,0:37:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他躺在橡皮艇裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:07.53,0:37:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從內側將入口用膠帶封住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:09.92,0:37:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後通過氣窗逃出房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:14.74,0:37:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著從二樓的天窗利用剛才的方法把水引入
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:19.06,0:37:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再迅速回到一樓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:20.53,0:37:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從氣窗鑽進去 再從內側將氣窗封住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:24.32,0:37:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不封死的話 水會從縫隙中流走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:28.90,0:37:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來只要小心不讓屍體沾到水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:32.79,0:37:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地等待水蓄滿就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:36.14,0:37:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水位不斷升高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:37.53,0:37:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當到達橫樑正下方的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:40.21,0:37:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手就將屍體綁在橫樑上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:42.17,0:37:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從容地從這個天窗逃出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:46.51,0:37:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他是怎麼將水排出的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:49.28,0:37:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用留在現場的斧子從外面把氣窗打破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:53.60,0:37:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:54.44,0:37:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我估計這個房間的容積是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:56.12,0:37:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面長2.7公尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:57.82,0:37:59.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間高度約為10公尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:00.09,0:38:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2.7公尺×2.7公尺×10公尺 就是72.9立方公尺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:07.31,0:38:09.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為水的比重是1
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:09.85,0:38:11.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灌滿整個房間的水的重量是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:12.23,0:38:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,72.9噸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:14.70,0:38:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦在積蓄了如此龐大的水量的房間底部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:17.43,0:38:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打破一個小洞的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:19.07,0:38:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會怎樣大家都清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:22.23,0:38:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個氣窗一旦產生裂縫之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:24.78,0:38:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計會產生9.8×10的4次方帕斯卡的強大壓力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:29.98,0:38:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股強大的水勢輕易就能在牆上破開一個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:33.77,0:38:35.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是個大洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:37.03,0:38:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9.8×10的4次方帕斯卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:39.87,0:38:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:40.95,0:38:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是能把卡車都推翻的強大力量啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:44.80,0:38:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:46.00,0:38:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以雖然破壞出了那麼大的一個洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:48.19,0:38:51.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附近卻找不到被沖破的牆壁和木板的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:51.62,0:38:52.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被沖走的木板碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:53.03,0:38:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南在寺下的樹林裡找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:56.62,0:38:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柯南啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:59.17,0:39:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:03.41,0:39:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:04.51,0:39:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黏著膠帶的氣窗碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:07.71,0:39:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 到底是誰幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:10.67,0:39:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把水排完只需要不到10秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:14.09,0:39:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要把水蓄滿就不一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:16.87,0:39:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天窗流進來的水量是水龍頭的五六倍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:21.23,0:39:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一小時的水量是10立方公尺的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:25.41,0:39:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要蓄滿72.9立方公尺的水就需要7個小時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:32.00,0:39:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住持的死亡推斷時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:34.35,0:39:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是昨晚的十點至十二點之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:37.35,0:39:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後發現屍體的時間是早上八點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:41.92,0:39:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除去準備手法的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:44.00,0:39:49.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及水被排完後清理現場的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:49.45,0:39:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手從昨晚十二點至今晨六點這六個小時內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:52.26,0:39:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都待在這個房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:55.85,0:39:59.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這跟兇手到底有什麼關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:59.48,0:40:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀念師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:01.68,0:40:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:03.00,0:40:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨晚在自己房間看書一直看到三點是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:08.16,0:40:08.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:09.08,0:40:10.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該也聽見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:11.18,0:40:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在昨晚兩點左右
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:12.59,0:40:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被廁所裡的天狗面具驚嚇到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:14.63,0:40:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個人所發出的慘叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:17.87,0:40:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫聲到底是誰發出的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:20.37,0:40:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:22.45,0:40:24.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀…秀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:24.16,0:40:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我當然聽到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:26.41,0:40:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小蘭小姐發出的尖叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:30.38,0:40:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也嚇了一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:31.83,0:40:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蘭小姐膽小也是沒辦法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:34.29,0:40:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀…秀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:35.51,0:40:36.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:37.66,0:40:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀念師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:39.24,0:40:41.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時發出慘叫的並不是小蘭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:43.03,0:40:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:47.69,0:40:50.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒聽到也是正常的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:50.56,0:40:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你在水聲隆隆的這個房間裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:52.81,0:40:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待了一個晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:55.56,0:40:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這算不上什麼證據啊 毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:59.39,0:41:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要確定的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:01.03,0:41:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就在警官你手裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:03.64,0:41:04.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個碎片嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:05.04,0:41:06.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水排完後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:06.51,0:41:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房內的犯罪痕跡雖然可以被湮滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:09.85,0:41:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但被沖走的這個碎片上的證據卻無法毀滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:13.99,0:41:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:14.83,0:41:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是兇手唯一忘記回收的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:20.52,0:41:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算賭上我的偵探生涯也在所不惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:24.01,0:41:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黏在這碎片的膠帶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:26.96,0:41:28.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定留有某樣東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:28.94,0:41:29.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秀念師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:30.41,0:41:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你的指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:34.11,0:41:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是秀念是一年前才到寺廟的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:37.73,0:41:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作案手法和兩年前一樣的話 兇手應該是同一個人才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:41.17,0:41:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能是秀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:43.19,0:41:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想兩年前的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:44.93,0:41:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是住持犯下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:47.40,0:41:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這次用的是同一個手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:50.33,0:41:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木板上的切口很老舊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:52.72,0:41:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最怕往事曝光的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:55.47,0:41:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是住持
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:57.87,0:41:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:58.97,0:42:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的直覺準確的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:01.49,0:42:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前被殺的忠念師父和秀念師父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:05.73,0:42:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是兄弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:08.57,0:42:09.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:09.75,0:42:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠念是我如假包換的親哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:14.98,0:42:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒發現也是很正常的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:17.65,0:42:20.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我隱姓埋名 通過認識的寺廟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:20.74,0:42:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才找到這裡來並做個修行僧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:24.50,0:42:25.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來這個寺廟的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:26.41,0:42:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:27.39,0:42:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是解開我哥的死因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:29.86,0:42:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及找出殺我哥哥的真兇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:32.63,0:42:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我花了半年的時間拼命在寺裡搜尋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:36.12,0:42:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然知道了作案手法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:38.14,0:42:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一直找不出兇手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:40.42,0:42:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為大家都閉口不提那天的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:44.32,0:42:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:45.63,0:42:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天偵探先生來了 我才終於了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:48.42,0:42:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到住持奇怪的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:50.40,0:42:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立刻就明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:52.41,0:42:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:53.62,0:42:54.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了住持的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:55.14,0:42:57.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想向睡前稍有醉意的住持問個清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:57.58,0:42:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他居然滔滔不絕的全都說出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:00.21,0:43:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒察覺到我就是忠念的弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:03.17,0:43:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他之所以殺死哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:05.19,0:43:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為不想讓哥哥破壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:06.92,0:43:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孫女菊乃小姐和大寺廟的繼承人的婚事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:12.98,0:43:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為菊乃小姐和我哥哥已經打算要一起私奔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:18.68,0:43:20.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這些都不重要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:20.93,0:43:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚我勸住持去自首
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:23.41,0:43:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到住持他卻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:25.51,0:43:27.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都已經是兩年前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:27.64,0:43:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,證據早就不存在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:31.85,0:43:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且多虧那個事件 我們寺現在也是聲名大噪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:37.97,0:43:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是霧天狗出沒的寺廟啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:43.98,0:43:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到他這麼說 我就失去了理智
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:46.66,0:43:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用房裡的繩子一把勒住他的脖子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:49.17,0:43:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他給殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:51.45,0:43:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:52.82,0:43:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像兩年前住持勒死哥哥一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:56.44,0:43:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了讓他看起來是上吊自殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:59.45,0:44:00.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還特意背對著他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:01.11,0:44:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當屍體倒在我眼前時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:03.23,0:44:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有選擇的餘地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:05.52,0:44:09.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能用住持兩年前使用的手法來掩飾罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:12.40,0:44:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很遺憾 偵探先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:15.20,0:44:16.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:16.76,0:44:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前就造訪這座山泥寺的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:20.56,0:44:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:23.01,0:44:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:57.32,0:46:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次破案你都會讓我大吃一驚啊 毛利老弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:01.59,0:46:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真不知道你對物理那麼有研究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:05.03,0:46:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:06.20,0:46:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘記啦 爸爸你剛才不是說了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:08.18,0:46:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕斯卡什麼什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:10.39,0:46:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕斯卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:11.80,0:46:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:14.89,0:46:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白乾是中國酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:16.52,0:46:17.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐斯卡是寶塚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:18.28,0:46:19.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rascal是小浣熊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:20.05,0:46:22.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕斯卡是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:24.45,0:46:26.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們說的是那本電視雜誌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:28.37,0:46:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:29.79,0:46:31.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是Telepal
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:31.61,0:46:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也只有最後一個音一樣而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:37.39,0:46:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶器是盆栽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:40.88,0:46:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你這小鬼不要每次都妨礙調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:45.80,0:46:47.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在有嫌疑的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:47.68,0:46:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是土橋先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:49.16,0:46:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來是夫人妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:53.12,0:46:56.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這好像是從下面用堅硬物體敲打的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:57.29,0:46:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兇手除了他沒有別人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:00.61,0:47:01.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:02.02,0:47:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謎樣兇器殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:06.25,0:47:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:08.68,0:47:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:11.23,0:47:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回即將邁入新學期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:13.07,0:47:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不要遲到喔
